# Product Overview

**Lules Market** is a comprehensive local business platform that enables small businesses to showcase their products and services online while providing customers with an easy way to discover and connect with local merchants.

## Core Features

### For Businesses
- Secure authentication with Better-Auth
- Product management with image uploads
- Three-tier subscription system (Free, Basic, Premium)
- Business profile management with social media integration
- Analytics and performance tracking
- Survey system for customer feedback
- Featured products for Premium subscribers

### For Customers
- Public product catalog browsing
- Advanced search and filtering
- Direct contact via WhatsApp, phone, email, and social media
- Anonymous survey participation

## Business Model
- **Free Plan**: Up to 5 products, basic profile
- **Basic Plan**: $9.99 USD - Up to 20 products, basic analytics
- **Premium Plan**: $29.99 USD - Unlimited products, advanced analytics, featured products, priority search placement

## Target Market
Small local businesses looking to establish an online presence and customers seeking local products and services.